    "Name" text NULL,
    "Quantity" integer NULL,

    "UpdateDate" timestamp with time zone NULL,

    "ProductDetailsId" integer NOT NULL,

    CONSTRAINT "FK_Products_ProductDetails_ProductDetailsId" FOREIGN KEY ("ProductDetailsId") REFERENCES "ProductDetails" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Products_ProductImage_ProductImageId" FOREIGN KEY ("ProductImageId") REFERENCES "ProductImage" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Products_ProductOffers_ProductOffersId" FOREIGN KEY ("ProductOffersId") REFERENCES "ProductOffers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
);

INNER JOIN "ProductDetails" AS p0 ON p."ProductDetailsId" = p0."Id"
INNER JOIN "ProductOffers" AS p1 ON p."ProductOffersId" = p1."Id"
INNER JOIN "ProductImage" AS p2 ON p."ProductImageId" = p2."Id"
